Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫南千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.25,0:00:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三姐妹的小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時覺得姐姐有一個就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無奈是三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:24.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}今天全國以晴天為主…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  好好的吐我槽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是早已起床了啊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被爐裡睡覺會感冒的喲什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:33.22,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這就是二女兒夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人如其名  如夏日陽光一樣讓人厭煩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼能引以為傲的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會是在想些什麼失禮的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒在想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得「夏奈今天也好精神啊」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,0:00:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖暖的暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.36,0:01:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種依賴被爐的生活打算持續到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被爐卻不用  對它可是很失禮的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.53,0:01:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.47,0:01:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好的話  來吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.62,0:01:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞錯了  這位是大女兒春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人如其名  如春日陽光一樣溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是引以為傲的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼也不能在被爐裡換衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐也請說說她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香的外套再放裡面暖暖麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋的制服已經暖好了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙打算依賴被爐生活到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:01:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被爐卻不用  對它可是很失禮的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  快點換好衣服來吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.74,0:02:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  今天也要精精神神地去上學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天會返還試卷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼  肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不休息可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要管我了你們先走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試成績要給我看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算今天休息考試成績也不會變  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出門嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:17.40,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(800,300)}春天的開始、南家的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還是那麼充滿人情味的絕妙分數
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可能不會令春香滿意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回考試不扭轉現狀就不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  找人教我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教我功課
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  夏奈不會認真學的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的我可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了我這認真的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  現在沒戴眼鏡看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  好奇怪  剛才還戴著的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:05:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子沒有回應我的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  去海邊吧去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋想去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求別人的時候  比起認真來純真才更重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪  美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高和我家的千秋差不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  純樸的眼神很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然這麼說雖然很失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成績不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼突然也太失禮了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個讓你提高成績的好提議
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  教美雪功課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來我家教就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:06:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好很棒喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我看上的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  這裡教我下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己稍微動動腦筋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  這裡教我下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼光偏袒美雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了教美雪的功課才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  不要那麼生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過拜託別人得到想要的只適用於小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠自己的力量去達成目的這才是學習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如夏奈所說的我要靠自己的力量努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個氣勢  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  降了一分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然光靠一個人的力量是不行的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類不互相幫助是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了夏奈  我第一次得了100分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要去做就能成功的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我長高的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以  不過要教我功課
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類要互相幫助才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.33,0:00:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  教我功課
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
